OL,3,CCity with largest spike in road deaths
OL,4,Cin South East revealed
OL,6,FNew research has revealed the city in
OL,7,Fthe South East with the highest rise
OL,8,Fin injuries and road deaths in 2024.
OL,10,FFigures released by the charity Brake
OL,11,Ffound Southampton saw the biggest
OL,12,Fincrease, with incidents up by almost
OL,13,Fa fifth.
OL,15,FFigures show nearly 5,000 people were
OL,16,Fkilled or seriously injured across the
OL,17,FSouth last year. It also says speed
OL,18,Fwas a factor in 59% of all road deaths
OL,19,Fin 2024.
