OL,3,CCity with largest spike in road deaths
OL,4,Cin South East revealed
OL,6,FThere were similar increases in ten of
OL,7,Fthe region's authorities, including
OL,8,FKent and East Sussex, where road
OL,9,Fdeaths and serious injuries were also
OL,10,Fup.
OL,12,FThe charity, Brake, released the
OL,13,Ffigures as part of its road safety
OL,14,Fawareness week, a national campaign
OL,15,Fcalling on people to drive more
OL,16,Fcarefully and the government to make
OL,17,Froads safer.
