OL,3,CCity with largest spike in road deaths
OL,4,Cin South East revealed
OL,6,FIt wants safety features like advanced
OL,7,Femergency braking and intelligent
OL,8,Fspeed assistance to be made mandatory
OL,9,Ffor all new vehicles sold in the UK,
OL,10,Fin line with regulations which are
OL,11,Falready in place in the European Union.
OL,13,FRoss Moorlock, Chief Executive at
OL,14,FBrake, said: "This year, we have put
OL,15,Fvehicle safety at the very heart of
OL,16,FRoad Safety Week, because we know that
OL,17,Fwhoever we are, and however we travel,
OL,18,Fthe safety of the vehicles we use is
OL,19,Fcritical to road safety.
