OL,3,CCity with largest spike in road deaths
OL,4,Cin South East revealed
OL,6,F"When we look back at the introduction
OL,7,Fof seatbelts and airbags, for example,
OL,8,Fthe impact they have had on reducing
OL,9,Froad deaths and injuries is staggering.
OL,11,F"We know that modern vehicle
OL,12,Ftechnology, with automated driver
OL,13,Fassistance systems, has the potential
OL,14,Fto have the same transformational
OL,15,Fimpact.
OL,17,F"There is simply no good reason why
OL,18,Fany new vehicle sold in the UK should
OL,19,Fnot to be fitted with the latest
OL,20,Fgeneration, life-saving safety
OL,21,Ffeatures as standard.
