OL,3,CCity with largest spike in road deaths
OL,4,Cin South East revealed
OL,6,F"Safety features such as intelligent
OL,7,Fspeed assistance and automated
OL,8,Femergency braking can play a crucial
OL,9,Frole in preventing crashes and
OL,10,Freducing the risk of death and serious
OL,11,Finjury on our roads, but only if we
OL,12,Fkeep them switched on!
OL,14,F"This Road Safety Week, I call on
OL,15,Feveryone who drives to find out more
OL,16,Fabout the safety features in your
OL,17,Fvehicle, and I urge you to use them,
OL,18,Fto help keep yourself and the people
OL,19,Fyou share the road with as safe as
OL,20,Fpossible."
